title: Intervention In-Depth - Pregnant & Addicted
description:
Intervention In-Depth focuses on one phenomenon surrounding addiction, explores its impact through addicts, and informs about the drug/problem in question. Intervention Pregnant and Addicted follows four women, addicted to drugs, that can harm the babies they're having. Centered at the Nexus Recovery Center in Dallas, Tex., Pregnant & Addicted shows the difficulty of the tasks of fighting addiction and motherhood. 
According to IMDB, this episode was released April 2011, meaning episode 15 of season 10?
